description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 60, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 60, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Box for East, Nine Lives for South, and 3 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70601-94934-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [60 Votes, Common]
